## Overview

There are so many devices that could be considered robots and technology that works with robots that it is hard to name them all.

On this page, you will find links to a variety of robots and devices.  Explore their uses and how you might use them your them in your classroom to help your students better understand human computer interaction, problem solving, and coding. The following resources can be used to help put robotics into context: 

